                <h2>Updated rpm packages fix security vulnerabilities</h2>

                Publication date: 14 Dec 2014<br />
                Type: security<br />
                Affected Mageia releases :
                
                
                
                
                <a href="4.html">4</a>
                
                <br />

                
                
                CVE:
                
                
                
                <a href="CVE-2013-6435.html">CVE-2013-6435</a>
                
